President Amin Gemayel named Sunni MoslemEducation Minister Selim Hoss as acting prime ministerfollowing the assassination of Premier Rashid Karami, apresidential palace statement said.    "After consultations by President Amin Gemayel withpolitical and religious leaders the president decided to nameSelim Hoss as acting prime minister," said the statementbroadcast on local radio stations.    Moslem leaders proposed Hoss, a former premier, as actingprime minister after Karami died of injuries from a bomb thatexploded aboard his helicopter. Reuter&#3;